{
  "id": "adv_card_smr_09_03",
  "title": "奥山すみれ 3話 頑張ったご褒美に",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_03-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "ご主人様、どうしても行ってしまわれるのですか……？\n三年も……それに外国は、あまりにも遠過ぎます……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Master‚ must you really go…?\nThree years… to a foreign country… it's too far…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "僕の肩には社員の生活がかかっているからね\n海外の技術を習得して、事業を回さなければならない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I have the livelihood of my employees on my shoulders.\nI have to learn the technology overseas and keep the business going.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.4333337148,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 24.7666646321
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_03-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "ご主人様、実は、私、ずっと……お慕い――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Master‚ actually‚ I’ve always… admired――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.7666646321,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 33.6666683196
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_03-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "……いえ、なんでもありません\nお気をつけて、行ってらっしゃいませ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…No‚ never mind.\nPlease be careful‚ and have a safe trip.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.4333354949,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 44.000000763
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "オッケー、ストップだ\n秘めた恋心をうまく表現出来てると思う",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay‚ cut!\nI think you expressed your hidden feelings well.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.2666690826,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 49.5666674297
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_03-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "本当ですか？　はぁ……良かったです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Really? Sigh… I’m glad.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.5666674297,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 53.6666674297
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_03-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "それに{user}さんも\nとっても演技が上手になりましたね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And you‚ {user}-san‚\nhave gotten so much better at acting!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.6000024159,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "お、俺のことはいいよ。……とにかく\n今日からクランクインだ。すみれ、準備は出来てるか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-it’s fine‚ don’t worry about me… Anyway‚\nfilming starts today. Sumire‚ are you ready?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 66.3999961854
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_03-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　あの日、{user}さんに\n迷いを吹き飛ばしてもらいましたから、やれます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes! I can do it‚ because\n{user}-san helped me overcome my doubts!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.366664505,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 72.7999961854
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "もうすぐ撮影が始まる時間だ\nこの先、俺は見ていることしか出来ない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's almost time for the shoot to start.\nFrom now on‚ all I can do is watch.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.5999978383,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 81.8999978383
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_03-smr007.m4a",
      "text": "はい、見ていて下さい\n今日が役者、奥山すみれの復活の日です……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ please watch me.\nToday is the day that actress Okuyama Sumire makes her comeback…！",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.8999978383,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 87.2166603089
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_03-smr008.m4a",
      "text": "ご主人様、今日はお庭でお仕事ですか？\n少しは休憩をとって、お体を気遣って下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Master‚ are you working in the garden today?\nPlease take a break and take care of yourself.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.7000039418,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_03-smr009.m4a",
      "text": "ご主人様が倒れたら……\n私まで路頭に迷ってしまうじゃないですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you collapse‚ Master…\n…I’ll be out on the streets too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.2333372752,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（演技素人の俺でも分かる……すみれは凄い）\n（子役の頃より、ずっとずっとうまくなってる）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Even I‚ a complete acting novice‚ can tell… Sumire is amazing.）\n（She’s become so much better than when she was a child actor.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.5333438873,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_03-smr010.m4a",
      "text": "――ええ、今年も桜が綺麗に咲きましたね\nすぐに散ってしまうから、私もよく見ておかないと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Yes‚ the cherry blossoms are blooming beautifully again this year.\nThey’ll scatter soon‚ so I should take a good look while I can.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.2333438873,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（ベテランの共演者達の中、一歩も引いてないどころか）\n（時にアドリブまで入れて、堂々と立ち回ってる）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Not only is she holding her own among veteran actors…）\n（…She’s even improvising sometimes‚ and acting with confidence.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.7000095367,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_03-smr011.m4a",
      "text": "私の故郷ではきっとまだ桜は咲いてはおりませんが――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m sure the cherry blossoms haven’t bloomed yet in my hometown――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.83332901,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_03-smr012.m4a",
      "text": "実家から駅までの道が綺麗な桜並木で\nそこを歩くのが大好きでした……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But the road from my house to the station is lined with beautiful cherry blossom trees‚\nand I loved walking along it…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.1333215076,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_03-smr013.m4a",
      "text": "本当に綺麗なのです\nいつかご主人様と一緒に、歩いてみたい――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s truly beautiful.\nI wish I could walk there with you someday‚ Master――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.6333113351,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7399.9949136999985,
          "startTime": 158.0333062488
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 157.4499712626
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_03-smr014.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さーん！　聞いて下さい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san~! You won’t believe this!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 158.5333117167,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "撮影初日、お疲れ様。走ると危ないぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good work on your first day of filming. Be careful when you’re running.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 162.0333147685,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 166.4999814351
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_03-smr015.m4a",
      "text": "さっき、撮影が終わってから\n監督さんが私の所に来て下さって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Just now‚ after the shoot ended‚\nthe director came to me‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 168.5999729155,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_03-smr016.m4a",
      "text": "私の演技のこと、すっごく褒めてくれたんです\nそれに、偏見を持っていて悪かったって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and he praised my acting! He said it was amazing!\nAnd he said he was sorry for having been prejudiced…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 176.5999729155,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 180.4666501363
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "すみれがこの辛い状況をよく耐えて\n実力を発揮出来たからだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s because you endured this difficult situation‚ Sumire‚\nand showed your true potential.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 183.0666467029,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_09_03-smr017.m4a",
      "text": "共演者さん達の陰口も、ピタリとなくなりました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The other actors have also stopped talking behind my back.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 185.3333239238,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 189.8999905904
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
